<div class="entryuserpic"><img src="http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/3907503/556230" alt="" height="100" width="100"  /></div></div>

<div class="entrycontent">I only ever played Oregon Trail as a kid in middle school, on the Apple IIc machines they had in the computer lab. At the time, I felt like the machine was ancient but looking back I see the machine had been on the market for less than two years at that point. Odd.<br /><br />Anyway, I don't ever recall being able to beat Oregon Trail as a kid. When I think about, I seem to remember thinking it was impossible to win the game. I should definitely try it again, though.</div>

